data.description: This home has everything you've been looking for! This one-story home offers 4 bedrooms 2 1/2 bathrooms, granite counter tops, stainless appliances, wood shutters, water softener and much more!  The backyard is fully landscaped and spacious with plenty of lighting for great entertainment! It is conveniently located with great access to many shops, great schools, restaurants, as well as a neighborhood park! Schedule your showing today!
